name: Shop - UI Kit
description:
This UI Kit is a perfect fit for you to:

  • start new project (you can use the foundation component for your project, or simply redesign the existing component)
  • code it into an existing app (there is design example, complete with the flow)
  • and more.


Enjoy this freebies. Feel free to reach me through email to share your thoughts and comments.


Also, you can buy me a coffee!
